{"tid":1545404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚9月6號，有狗狗喺沙田凱悅酒店結婚","createTime":"2019-09-06T01:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T22:37:04.000Z","uid":42107,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4bbed3da433d442043db9746c793fffe7af70883","tid":1545404,"uid":42107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:46:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日對狗男女於9月6日，即今日晚上6點 沙田凱悅酒店擺酒</span></span></strong>，<br />\n去完祝賀佢地再坐火車去太子獻花時間岩岩好🥰<br />\n<br />\n狗名：吳庭棟 Roy Ng<br />\n狗隊編號：11448 做機場特警 速龍<br />\n老豆搵仔編號：<br />\n電話號碼：65161328<br />\n地址：屯門<br />\n身分證：<br />\nemail: <br />\n生日日期: 3月9日<br />\n伴侶：陳嘉穎 深藍仁安醫院私家病房護士專勾人男友/老公 ig：kawing1225<br />\n仔女：<br />\n父：吳扭妹<br />\n母：沈聯鳳<br />\n家姐: <br />\n中學：屯門深培中學<br />\n大學：<br />\nFacebook：roy.ng.75<br />\nInstagram：roy_ng_0309<br />\nTG: <br />\n出沒地點及生活習慣: 揸寶馬扮有錢仔，部車有改裝，但從來無俾人抄牌，官官相衛佢老味。<br />\n威水史：娶有錢護士老婆，食軟飯入豪門，點知條女老早俾綠帽佢戴仲on99同人結婚，條女同另一男人結婚相都影埋喇。另外，條友做速龍日日OT，人工多左仲不知幾開心話打人有錢收。佔中時係黃，而家變節。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對狗男女將於2019年9月6日晚上6點 沙田凱悅酒店擺酒</span></span></strong>，各位手足星期五晚去賀賀佢地，記得話俾隻狗知佢頂警帽好綠。Print 定佢老婆同契家佬影啲結婚相派俾賓客炒慶個場，既合法又開心，恭喜恭喜。<br />\n<br />\n老婆同契家佬結婚相上撚哂網， 狗Roy 仲 on99<br />\n<a href=\"http://mrkwedding.com/index.php?mid=epilogue&amp;category_alias=groombride-pre-wedding-story&amp;document_alias=korea-pre-wedding-wing-couple-cherry-blossom-photography\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrkwedding.com%2Findex.php%3Fmid%3Depilogue%26category_alias%3Dgroombride-pre-wedding-story%26document_alias%3Dkorea-pre-wedding-wing-couple-cherry-blossom-photography&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84HwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=661746ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mrkwedding.com/index.php?mid=epilogue&amp;category_alias=groombride-pre-wedding-story&amp;document_alias=korea-pre-wedding-wing-couple-cherry-blossom-photography</a>"},{"pid":"ab8e31ddb9deafc97b1fa0aa02d341e1c84a6aad","tid":15454